  <content>
The Anchor macro implements the Confluence Anchro macro by bridging it to the [[XWiki id macro&gt;&gt;url:https://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/Id%20Macro]]. It supports the same parameter "name"

{{anchor name="test" /}}
== Example ==

Anchor "test"

{{code}}
{{anchor name="test" /}}
{{/code}}

Scroll down to see a link to the anchor:

